section.def:
licence
                (許可證) means a licence issued under section
                5;

licensee
                (持證人) means a person occupying land under a
            licence or under a licence or permit granted or issued under any other Ordinance;

structure
                (構築物) includes a stilt, platform, fence and any
            other thing erected on or over land;

subsection.def:
carriageway
                    (車路) means a street or part of a street over
                which the public has a right of way for the passage of motor vehicles;

paragraph.content:
the duration of the initial period of an emergency excavation according to
                        section 10C(5) if he exercises the Director of Highways’ power
                    under section 10C(4);

the duration of an extended period of an excavation permit extended under
                        section 10A(3) if he exercises the Director of Highways’ power
                    under that section;

the duration of an extended period of an excavation permit extended under
                        section 10A(4) if he exercises the Director of Highways’ power
                    under that section;

the duration of an extended period of an excavation permit extended under
                        section 10D(4) if he exercises the Director of Highways’ power
                    under that section;

the duration of an extended period of an excavation permit extended under
                        section 10F(2) if he exercises the Director of Highways’ power
                    under that section;

whether an extension is caused by reasons mentioned in section
                        10L(1)(b) if he exercises the Director of Highways’ power under
                        section 10L(1);

whether the reasons mentioned in section 10L(1)(b) hindered the
                    progress of an excavation to which the excavation permit relates if he exercises
                    the Director of Highways’ power under section 10L(1);

td.p:
Director of Highways in the case of unleased land which is a street;
                                or the Director of Lands in the case of unleased land, other than
                                streets
